    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Smicromyrme plantourianus, female, dorsal habitus, variation. A Ribeira do Torgal, 15.vii.2019 B Carvoeira, 1.vii.2021 (‘curtiventris’; RMC1338) C Miranda do Douro, 16.viii.2022 (RMC1693) D Miranda do Douro, 18.viii.2022 (RMC1717) E Miranda do Douro, 18.viii.2022 (RMC1708) F Virtudes, 22.ix.2022 (RMC1749) G Carvoeira, 4.vii.2021 (RMC1344). Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
