<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10171090>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Smicromyrme plantourianus, female, pygidium, variation. A Carvoeira, 4.vii.2021 (RMC1341) B Miranda do Douro, 18.viii.2022 (RMC1717) C Virtudes, 22.ix.2022 (RMC1749) D Miranda do Douro, 16.viii.2022 (RMC1704) E Carvoeira, 14.viii.2018 (‘curtiventris’; RMC594) F Carvoeira, 14.viii.2019 (RMC1014). Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
